org.sd.extract
Class PivotContextExtractor

java.lang.Object
  org.sd.extract.PivotContextExtractor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Extractor
public class PivotContextExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Extractor

An extractor to pull contextual strings from a document surrounding (before) pivot extractions. Note that the pivot extractors must set a property on their extracted text nodes with key="extracted", value=[extractionType].

Author:
Spence Koehler
